339
00:16:22,470 --> 00:16:24,200
Are you here to see a doctor too?

340
00:16:24,710 --> 00:16:26,510
Who is the patient?

341
00:16:26,590 --> 00:16:27,520
She's a patient.

342
00:16:28,150 --> 00:16:28,840
You?

343
00:16:31,470 --> 00:16:32,140
Miss,

344
00:16:32,390 --> 00:16:35,790
