376
00:17:40,140 --> 00:17:40,710
You...

377
00:17:41,030 --> 00:17:42,160
All right, Lingsha.

378
00:17:42,190 --> 00:17:42,830
I know.

379
00:17:42,950 --> 00:17:44,090
You will definitely say

380
00:17:44,090 --> 00:17:46,090
