465
00:21:27,610 --> 00:21:29,780
My father’s name is Yun Tianqing.

466
00:21:30,700 --> 00:21:32,300
Your father is Yun Tianqing?

467
00:21:32,340 --> 00:21:33,670
Judging from your tone,

468
00:21:33,870 --> 00:21:35,200
