469
00:21:36,490 --> 00:21:38,020
Everyone knows your father

470
00:21:38,030 --> 00:21:39,510
in Qionghua.

471
00:21:40,000 --> 00:21:41,010
If that's the case,

472
00:21:41,010 --> 00:21:42,670
