487
00:22:11,080 --> 00:22:12,080
Please follow me.

488
00:22:12,340 --> 00:22:12,940
All right!

489
00:22:16,460 --> 00:22:17,260
Young man,

490
00:22:17,430 --> 00:22:18,670
you should know we are

491
00:22:18,750 --> 00:22:20,480
