543
00:24:35,850 --> 00:24:37,050
Thank you, Mr. Huaishuo.

544
00:24:37,050 --> 00:24:38,420
You're welcome, Mr. Yun.

545
00:24:38,420 --> 00:24:39,460
Uncle Ziying said

546
00:24:39,480 --> 00:24:41,580
