547
00:24:41,580 --> 00:24:42,220
Thank you.

548
00:24:42,780 --> 00:24:43,540
Tianhe.

549
00:24:44,590 --> 00:24:45,310
Mengli?

550
00:24:46,550 --> 00:24:47,530
Where is Lingsha?

551
00:24:47,530 --> 00:24:48,820
She hasn't recovered yet

552
00:24:48,820 --> 00:24:49,900
